The bundled critical-council protocol is an independent, domain-specific adaptation
of the three-stage deliberation pattern documented by karpathy/llm-council:
parallel first opinions, pseudonymized peer ranking, and chair synthesis.

Reference design:
https://github.com/karpathy/llm-council/commit/92e1fccb1bdcf1bab7221aa9ed90f9dc72529131

No source code from that upstream repository is included. The conceptual attribution
is retained because the reviewed revision had no detected license.
